Usecase Name         : Login
Participating Actors : Initiated by User
Entry Condition      : User must be "Signed-Up" to the WWDS.

Flow of Events : 
1)  User wants to use WWDS System's functions. Either by system or by  the WWDS system, user being directed to use login function.
2)  WWDS displays a "Log-In" page.
3)  User fills out following credentials. â€œUsername" and "Password"
4)  WWDS checks those credentials.
5)  WWDS closes the login form and reloads the WWDS page. 

Exit Condition : User logins successfully.
